Summary: Woke up to my son crying for a bottle. The wife took care of that and I laid in bed. I heard a weird sound fading in a out for 20 mins.
divs: sighting detailslaying in bed, hot as can be, because the family wanted to save money and sleep with the windows open. i couldn't fall back asleep because it was very humid that night. i heard a noise, not too loud, not too faint. the noise sounded sort of like a a\c compressor pulsing and humming. well been a hvac technician for 2 years working with compressors daily, this was no freon compressor i have ever heard. the noise was very distinct and i could tell what it was. the noise was a electrical humming with pulses in a out. i could tell it was above me, and not below me. i was sleeping on the 2nd floor of the house. after a few minutes you could hear it move to other locations. the only thing that i could think of was a ufo, and it was sitting there scanning us. finally after 20 minutes the noise got very faint, and disappeared. i was in shock after experiencing this. either this was a miliatry craft that doesn't use fuel, or it's gotta be a ufo. i have read up on mufon in the past, so i am a believer, but never thought this would happen to me. i would of have gotten up to look out the window, but i was in shock and could not move. also, as of 5\31\11 when i went to write this event. i checked the live event map on the site mufon.com and noticed a post that was from that same night and roughly the same location. that event was about 50 miles away.
